2010-05-01T19:00:00Z : Found it by anxie
An unscheduled visit this time and easy in the end. we had nothing 2 leave, but will give the gcoin a nice new home :) TFTC!

2010-04-25T19:00:00Z : Found it by danomalley
Possibly the quickest find I've ever had -- the coordinates were spot-on and I literally found it within 30 seconds of getting to the zero point. This place is only about 5 mins drive from my house, I'm amazed I never bothered to go pick up this cache before. TFTC!
Took: hair clip, balloon, whistle Left: beetle toy, mini skittle set, Kinder Surprise toy & geocoin

2009-07-19T19:00:00Z : Found it by Kersti.com
Out for a day of caching with JME1979 - this was our second find for the day and my 299th overall.
